content:
Invocable Actions in Insurance:

Create Accounts Invocable Action: Creates person account records for group census members.

Create Contacts Invocable Action: Creates contact records for group census members.

Create Portal Users Invocable Action: Creates user records with IsPortalUser property enabled for group census members.

Enroll Members Invocable Action: Creates insurance policies for primary members and their dependents by enrolling them into subscribed plans.

Generate User Inputs Invocable Action: Generates user inputs and fact ratings.

Rate Products Invocable Action: Rates insurance products as part of the Group Benefits Rating business process.
title: Salesforce Insurance Platform
